{"tid":2357992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再咁落去 連登離淪陷不遠了 分化 滲透愈來愈多（2）","createTime":"2021-01-07T23:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T02:44:15.000Z","uid":205928,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c0842e37199c7ec5a69132e5a871149b6bc552b3","tid":2357992,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T23:08:47.000Z","msg":"試當真出啲咁嘅片有咩居心。。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2357581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2357581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我夠膽講呢個post 入面大部份都係五毛 pr<br />\n少上連登嘅人好容易會中伏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95eb63d081e32d00e4bda96dc6520e1a07c6a70f","tid":2357992,"uid":205928,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T23:10:47.000Z","msg":"係五毛 pr 勢力愈來愈龐大<br />\n無孔不入<br />\n希望你以後謹言慎行吧<br />\n一有機會班友就會上綱上線 瘋狂批鬥<br />\n人格謀殺 係共匪慣用手法<br />\n暫時未諗到解決方法去應付呢啲網軍<br />\n所以我話連登離淪陷不遠就係咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f9863bfe390e01fb736be2ab95fcf4c6eefa80","tid":2357992,"uid":205928,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T23:11:37.000Z","msg":"佢地真係好撚顛<br />\n放負 批鬥 分化 扮黃 冷嘲熱諷乜柒都有<br />\n人數多到難以想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目的係搞爛連登 令到愈來愈少人用連登<br />\n佢地就贏 得閒仲可以批鬥黃絲人物<br />\n一舉幾得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那或成最後贏家"},{"pid":"257a78c43aaae44b78c59f0f6f1984a6a0453759","tid":2357992,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T23:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2980a7f5a4cd8d85dd79b78f1d0822a207c7951a","tid":2357992,"uid":205928,"lik